title: Type O Negative - World Coming Down [320kbs] ~~Renovatio~~
description:
World Coming Down is the fifth album by the Brooklyn band Type O Negative. from 1999.

As with the band's previous album, October Rust, this album also has a "joke intro": in this case, the intro, appropriately titled "Skip It", is 11 seconds of staccato band noise, meant to sound as if the listener's CD player is skipping. Cassette versions had the noise of a tape being "eaten" by the tape player. The track ends with what is presumably the guitarist, Kenny Hickey,
